-- MOVES-Kati Watson joins Salamanca Group's trust & fiduciary business
-- By Anet Josline Pinto in Bengaluru
-- Wed Dec 10, 2014 06:11AM EST
-- None



Dec 10 (Reuters) - Salamanca Group Holdings Ltd, a merchant banking and operational risk management business, appointed Kati Watson as senior trust manager and team head of its trust & fiduciary office based in Geneva.

The trust & fiduciary business also made three more appointments since its acquisition in February, Salamanca Group said.